  ('optician-moex-00404', 'optician', 'optician-moex-112-5e38135e', 'sub-optician-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關水晶體的胚胎發育，下列敘述何者正確？', '["次級水晶體纖維（secondarylensfiber）融合的前後縫合（anteriorandposteriorsuture）形成Y字型", "前後縫合（anteriorandposteriorsuture）形成Y字型方向一樣", "水晶體外囊（capsule）與水晶體的內皮細胞（endothelium）有關", "初級水晶體纖維（primarylensfiber）主要位在水晶體的後緣（posteriorlayer）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7d107214d300", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7e194b50ba52", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "110", "s": "0906", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼球構造與倫理法規概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-00405', 'optician', 'optician-moex-112-5e38135e', 'sub-optician-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於小樑網（trabecularmeshwork）的生理敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["小樑網位於眼後房", "年齡因素會引起小樑網結構的改變", "隅角鏡檢查（gonioscopy）可觀察到小樑網", "若細胞碎片或色素顆粒堆積於小樑網內可能會干擾房水的排出"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:28+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7d107214d300", "answer_pdf_sha1": "7e194b50ba52", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "110", "s": "0906", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼球構造與倫理法規概要", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
